@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@apiPrefix = /api/v1
@accessToken = your_access_token_here

### Get Properties
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/properties?whereTo=Mumbai&checkIn=2025-12-01&checkOut=2025-12-05&adults=2&childrens=1&rooms=1&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Properties - Sort by Price Low to High
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/properties?whereTo=Delhi&checkIn=2025-12-01&checkOut=2025-12-05&adults=2&childrens=1&rooms=1&page=1&limit=10&sortBy=price_low_to_high
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Properties - Sort by Price High to Low
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/properties?whereTo=Delhi&checkIn=2025-12-01&checkOut=2025-12-05&adults=2&childrens=1&rooms=1&page=1&limit=10&sortBy=price_high_to_low
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Properties - Search by Name
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/properties?whereTo=Delhi&checkIn=2025-12-01&checkOut=2025-12-05&adults=2&childrens=1&rooms=1&page=1&limit=10&search=luxury
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Properties - Search by Name with Sort
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/properties?whereTo=Delhi&checkIn=2025-12-01&checkOut=2025-12-05&adults=2&childrens=1&rooms=1&page=1&limit=10&search=villa&sortBy=price_low_to_high
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Random Properties
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/properties/random?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Property by ID
@propertyId = property_id_here

GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/properties/{{propertyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Create Property
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/properties
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "propertyName": "Ocean View Villa",
  "type": "villa",
  "address": {
    "fullAddress": "123 Beach Road, Goa",
    "zipCode": "403001"
  },
  "location": {
    "latitude": 15.2993,
    "longitude": 74.1240
  },
  "capacity": {
    "adults": 4,
    "childrens": 2
  },
  "noOfRooms": 2,
  "noOfBaths": 2,
  "basePrice": 5000,
  "totalUnits": 1,
  "amenties": ["Wifi", "Pool", "AC"],
  "description": "Beautiful 2BHK villa with ocean view",
  "coverImage": "https://example.com/image.jpg",
  "minimumRentalIncome": 50000,
  "saleTarget": 200000,
  "kycDocument": "https://example.com/kyc.pdf"
}

### Update Property (Basic Info)
PUT {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/properties
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "propertyId": "{{propertyId}}",
  "propertyName": "Ocean View Villa Updated",
  "basePrice": 5500
}

### Update Property Details (Media, Spaces, etc.)
PUT {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/properties/details
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "propertyId": "{{propertyId}}",
  "locationDescription": "Located near the famous Baga beach.",
  "faqs": [
    { "question": "Is breakfast included?", "answer": "Yes" }
  ]
}

### Toggle Property Active Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}{{apiPrefix}}/properties/toggle-active
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "propertyId": "{{propertyId}}"
}
